<section class="lp-section a-fade-up" id="cost">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-tag" style="text-align:center;">The cost of doing nothing</div>
    <h2 style="text-align:center;margin:0 auto 8px;">Auto-renewal isn't a convenience. It's a £4bn tax on not paying attention.</h2>
    <p class="section-sub" style="text-align:center;margin:0 auto 36px;">Every provider is incentivised to make renewal silent. Here's what that adds up to for UK households.</p>
    <div class="stat-hero a-fade-up tilt-wrap">
      <div class="stat-hero-card tilt-card">
        <div class="stat-hero-figure" data-count="4000000000">£4bn</div>
        <div class="stat-hero-label">Annual loyalty penalty across UK households</div>
        <span class="stat-hero-src">CMA 2019</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-hero-card tilt-card">
        <div class="stat-hero-figure" data-count="560000000">£560m</div>
        <div class="stat-hero-label">Lost to car insurance auto-renewal alone each year</div>
        <span class="stat-hero-src">Motoring Research 2025</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-hero-card tilt-card">
        <div class="stat-hero-figure" data-count="47">47%</div>
        <div class="stat-hero-label">Of UK drivers don't check their renewal before it hits</div>
        <span class="stat-hero-src">Motoring Research 2025</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="lp-section lp-section-dark a-fade-up" id="how">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-tag" style="text-align:center;">How it works</div>
    <h2 style="text-align:center;margin:0 auto 8px;">One email forward, one clear verdict. That's the whole loop.</h2>
    <p class="section-sub" style="text-align:center;margin:0 auto 0;">perch. doesn't need your bank, your passwords, or your attention every day. Just the emails you'd ignore anyway.</p>
    <div class="steps tilt-wrap">
      <div class="step tilt-card">
        <span class="step-index">01</span>
        <h3>Forward it</h3>
        <div class="step-desc">Send us the renewal email, PDF, or screenshot. One forward, or batch a dozen in one go.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="step tilt-card">
        <span class="step-index">02</span>
        <h3>We extract it</h3>
        <div class="step-desc">Our AI reads the provider, the amount, the renewal date, and the price change — even from scanned documents.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="step tilt-card">
        <span class="step-index">03</span>
        <h3>You get a verdict</h3>
        <div class="step-desc">Renew, Cancel, or Renegotiate — with a clear reason and the deadline. You decide what to do next.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="step tilt-card">
        <span class="step-index">04</span>
        <h3>Monday digest</h3>
        <div class="step-desc">Every Monday morning, a 90-second summary of everything renewing this week. Peace of mind in your inbox.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

