<section class="lp-section lp-section-dark a-fade-up" id="not">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-tag" style="text-align:center;">Not another fintech app</div>
    <h2 style="text-align:center;margin:0 auto 8px;">We do one thing. That's the whole point.</h2>
    <p class="section-sub" style="text-align:center;margin:0 auto 36px;">If it sounds like a budgeting app, read again. We explicitly don't do the things that make other financial tools invasive, noisy, or conflicted.</p>
    <div class="not-grid tilt-wrap">
      <div class="not-card tilt-card">
        <div class="not-mark">✕</div>
        <h3>No bank linking</h3>
        <p>We never connect to your bank or card accounts. No read-only access, no API tokens, no "just this once" permissions. Your bank data stays with your bank.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="not-card tilt-card">
        <div class="not-mark">✕</div>
        <h3>No auto-cancel bots</h3>
        <p>We never act on your behalf. You get the verdict and the deadline. You make the call. We're a radar, not a robot with your login credentials.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="not-card tilt-card">
        <div class="not-mark">✕</div>
        <h3>No budgeting features</h3>
        <p>No spend categories, no net worth tracking, no charts about your coffee habit. That's a different product. We stay in our lane — renewals only.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

